<para style="p">For the chief musician; set to Shoshannim. A psalm of the sons of Korah. A maschil. A song of loves.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />My heart overflows on a good subject;</para>

<para style="q1">I will read aloud the words I have composed about the king;</para>

<para style="q1">my tongue is the pen of a ready writer.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />You are fairer than the children of mankind;</para>

<para style="q1">grace is poured onto your lips;</para>

<para style="q1">therefore we know that God has blessed you forever.</para>
